  <Subject Subject_ID="300191751">
    <Parent_Relationships>
      <Preferred_Parent>
        <Parent_Subject_ID>300253873</Parent_Subject_ID>
        <Relationship_Type>Parent/Child</Relationship_Type>
        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>time-related attributes [300253873], attributes and properties by specific type [300226808], Attributes and Properties (hierarchy name) [300123559], Physical Attributes Facet [300264087]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
      </Preferred_Parent>
    </Parent_Relationships>
    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The quality of existing or functioning for a long, indefinite period of time without significant change. Use especially with regard to situations and to nonmechanical properties of objects or materials, such as resistance of color to fading or resistance of paper to acid deterioration; regarding long-term resistance to mechanical wear, prefer "durability."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>La cualidad de existir o funcionar por un periodo largo, indefinido de tiempo sin cambios significativos. Use sobre todo con respecto a las condiciones y a las propiedades no mecánicas de objetos o materiales, como la resistencia del color a decolorarse o la resistencia del papel al deterioro por ácido; con respecto a la resistencia a largo plazo al uso mecánico, prefiera "durabilidad."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>De eigenschap voor een lange, onbepaalde tijd te bestaan of te werken, zonder noemenswaardige verandering. Vooral te gebruiken met betrekking tot situaties en tot niet-mechanische eigenschappen van voorwerpen of materialen, zoals de bestendigheid van kleur tegen verschieten of de bestendigheid van papier tegen achteruitgang door zuren; gebruik 'duurzaamheid' met betrekking tot langdurige bestendigheid tegen mechanische slijtage.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>存在或運作一段很長的，無限期時間而沒有顯著變化的特質。特別用以指情況與物件或材質之非機械性屬性，像是抗退色的色彩或抗酸性的紙張；至於長期抗機械性磨損，稱作「耐久性」。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000079740/AS-Academia Sinica data (2014-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
